nodes.text: The Inner Moon was a moon located in the Prakith system. It was one of two moons that orbited the planet Prakith and was closer to it than the other moon. It had no atmosphere and low gravity. In about 19 BBY, the ship Good Feeling crashed there, after being attacked by mynocks. However, after a group of Alderaanian Resistance operatives came to the rescue, the ship was able to leave the moon.
